T1  - When good investments go bad: The contraction in community bank lending after the 2008 GSE takeover
AU  - Rice, Tara
AU  - Rose, Jonathan
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 27
SP  - 68
EP  - 88
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/07/01/
