T1  - Should cross-border banking benefit from the financial safety net?
AU  - Bertay, Ata Can
AU  - Demirgüç-Kunt, Asli
AU  - Huizinga, Harry
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 27
SP  - 51
EP  - 67
